query:
SELECT distinct (t.id),
  t.public_spec,
  t.order_number
from exercise_tasks t
where t.exercise_slide_id in (
    SELECT id
    from exercise_slides s
    where s.exercise_id in (
        SELECT id
        from exercises e
        where exercise_type = $1
          AND e.chapter_id in (
            SELECT id
            from chapters c
            where c.course_module_id = $2
          )
      )
  )
  AND deleted_at IS NULL;
